						<summary>

						<p>On a stone set up near the Lakshmīnārāyaṇa-perumāḷ temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Īśvara, Phālguṇa śu. 5.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of land as <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> for conducting worship to the god Lakshmīnārāyaṇasvāmi at Iyaku <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Anantāchāryapuram by Rāchamalla Veṅgana and the several <hi rend="italic">ayyaṅgārs</hi> of the village.</p>						

						</summary>
